---
title: Quick Cheesy Harissa Chickpea Taquitos with Baby Leaf Salad
description: Meaning 'little taco', taquitos are one of the original Cal-Mex dishes, known for their crispy rolled up shells and tasty fillings. We've stuffed these with a delicious veggie filling made from chickpeas and spiced with harissa.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W27_UK_QV23454-3_Main_high-b7a3694c.jpg
